cs.SI, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.CY

This paper involves the use of social multimedia and natural language processing techniques to detect breaking news events from Wikipedia and social network sites. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also involves the creation of media galleries, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper involves the use of natural language processing techniques for text analysis, which falls under the categories of cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper involves the study of a specific event, the 2014 Winter Olympics, which falls under the category of cs.CY (Computers and Society).
